Review this cc.LayerGradient code for issues:

```typescript
const sky = new cc.LayerGradient(
    cc.color(135, 206, 250, 255),
    cc.color(25, 25, 112, 255),
    cc.p(0, -1)
);
this.addChild(sky, -1);

setInterval(() => {
    sky.setStartColor(cc.color(
        Math.random() * 255,
        Math.random() * 255,
        Math.random() * 255
    ));
