```typescript
declare namespace cc {
    class Layer extends Node {
        constructor();
        bake(): void;       // HTML5 only: cache children to bake sprite
        unbake(): void;     // HTML5 only: uncache
        isBaked(): boolean; // check if currently baked
    }
}
```

`cc.Layer` extends `cc.Node` and adds three HTML5-specific methods for render caching. `bake()` renders all children into a single cached texture for better draw-call performance. `unbake()` reverts to normal rendering. `isBaked()` returns the current state. These are no-ops on native platforms.

