Schedule a periodic update that increments the bar's percent:

```typescript
const bar = new ccui.LoadingBar('loading_bar.png', 0);
bar.setDirection(ccui.LoadingBar.TYPE_LEFT);
bar.setPosition(240, 100);
this.addChild(bar);

const label = new ccui.Text('Loading... 0%', 'Arial', 18);
label.setPosition(240, 140);
this.addChild(label);

let progress = 0;
this.schedule((dt: number) => {
    progress += dt * 20; // fill over ~5 seconds
    if (progress >= 100) {
        progress = 100;
        this.unschedule(arguments.callee);
        this.onLoadComplete();
    }
    bar.setPercent(progress);
    label.setString('Loading... ' + Math.floor(progress) + '%');
}, 0.05);
```

The director fires events at specific points in the frame loop:

```typescript
