Listen for these events using `cc.eventManager.addCustomListener`:

```typescript
// Execute code after all updates complete each frame
const listener = cc.eventManager.addCustomListener(
    cc.Director.EVENT_AFTER_UPDATE,
    (event: cc.Event) => {
        // Physics resolution, collision checking, etc.
        resolveCollisions();
    }
);

// Execute code after rendering
